    <p>
      My journey with computers began almost three decades ago when my dad brought home a <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Commodore_64">Commodore 64</a>. Since I wasn't a genius kid, my interactions with computers boiled down to smashing joysticks and copying listings from books and magazines.
    </p>

    <p>
